I don't have the heart to say yes.

354
00:28:38,416 --> 00:28:40,145
And, I don't have the courage
to say no.

355
00:28:40,285 --> 00:28:42,378
Okay, then send him over.

356
00:28:49,094 --> 00:28:53,155
Because of you both
I'm caught in the crossfire.

357
00:28:53,465 --> 00:28:55,194
Stop complaining!

358
00:28:55,400 --> 00:28:57,459
You are just caught
in the crossfire.

359
00:28:57,535 --> 00:29:00,026
We've been pushed into war.

360
00:29:00,105 --> 00:29:01,003
Keep running!

361
00:29:01,573 --> 00:29:04,371
Why has papa got him
to train with us?

362
00:29:04,442 --> 00:29:06,501
This pint-sized boy is no challenge.

363
00:29:06,578 --> 00:29:08,705
He looks like a 'TTSS' to me.

364
00:29:08,980 --> 00:29:10,038
What does that mean?

365
00:29:10,115 --> 00:29:12,106
Tall on Talk, Short on Strength.

366
00:29:16,955 --> 00:29:18,582
'TTSS'... is it?

367
00:29:35,206 --> 00:29:37,333
Go easy, I'm your little sister.

368
00:29:37,475 --> 00:29:38,373
Yes... yes!

369
00:29:48,219 --> 00:29:49,618
Don't mind me saying,

370
00:29:49,988 --> 00:29:51,319
