386
00:31:46,170 --> 00:31:47,034
Come on.

387
00:31:47,105 --> 00:31:48,265
Try again.

388
00:31:56,614 --> 00:31:59,310
Where's the strength in you?

389
00:32:02,620 --> 00:32:04,588
You are training the girls to wrestle,

390
00:32:04,722 --> 00:32:06,314
I didn't say anything.

391
00:32:06,524 --> 00:32:08,617
But I will not allow you to cook
chicken in my kitchen!

392
00:32:08,693 --> 00:32:10,320
Try and understand.

393
00:32:10,461 --> 00:32:12,429
Wrestlers require protein.

394
00:32:12,497 --> 00:32:14,021
I don't care!

395
00:32:14,098 --> 00:32:15,725
If meat is cooked in my kitchen,

396
00:32:16,000 --> 00:32:17,297
I will stop eating.

397
00:32:17,368 --> 00:32:19,427
You want your girls
to be weak wrestlers?

398
00:32:19,504 --> 00:32:21,028
I don't know anything.

399
00:32:21,105 --> 00:32:23,573
There's no way chicken will be
cooked in my kitchen!

400
00:32:27,145 --> 00:32:28,635
