won't ever complain.

475
00:36:45,503 --> 00:36:47,596
Just don't cut our hair, please.

476
00:36:47,672 --> 00:36:49,037
Please, papa.

477
00:36:50,608 --> 00:36:51,575
Cut it.

478
00:36:52,109 --> 00:36:52,734
Cut it?

479
00:36:53,778 --> 00:36:55,336
Can you grow it?

480
00:36:57,315 --> 00:36:58,577
Then cut it.

