500
00:39:44,648 --> 00:39:46,115
Age is catching up.

501
00:39:46,484 --> 00:39:47,451
No problem.

502
00:39:48,119 --> 00:39:49,677
We've finished today's training.

503
00:39:49,987 --> 00:39:51,352
Come, Babita.

504
00:39:57,495 --> 00:40:01,158
Countless light-bulbs were martyred.

505
00:40:02,400 --> 00:40:04,391
How come the bulb fuses everyday?

506
00:40:04,602 --> 00:40:05,660
