from the film 'Sholay'.

513
00:40:25,322 --> 00:40:27,085
Get out of here!

514
00:40:28,159 --> 00:40:32,289
I couldn't understand how
I had suddenly become so strong.

515
00:40:32,596 --> 00:40:35,565
