520
00:40:48,345 --> 00:40:49,778
M... mummy.

521
00:40:50,181 --> 00:40:52,149
Are you trying to embarrass me?

522
00:40:53,217 --> 00:40:54,582
Choose one.

523
00:40:55,052 --> 00:40:56,144
This one.

524
00:41:03,994 --> 00:41:05,393
Let me see.

525
00:41:07,731 --> 00:41:11,223
Finally,
my girls are looking like girls.

526
00:41:14,405 --> 00:41:16,396
Don't tell papa.

527
00:41:16,674 --> 00:41:18,505
Come home before 8pm.

