Sir, I want to buy a mat
for her to train on.

791
01:01:58,481 --> 01:02:00,176
She's playing well.

792
01:02:00,483 --> 01:02:01,609
If you support her today,

793
01:02:01,684 --> 01:02:03,515
then one day, she will
make the nation proud.

794
01:02:03,686 --> 01:02:05,517
Look, Mahavir Singh-ji,

795
01:02:05,621 --> 01:02:08,055
we get this much
funding for sports.

796
01:02:08,691 --> 01:02:10,454
Wrestling gets this much.

797
01:02:10,760 --> 01:02:12,227
Keep aside gents wrestling,

798
01:02:12,295 --> 01:02:15,731
then remove coaching, dieting,
traveling, equipment, etc.

799
01:02:15,998 --> 01:02:17,989
All that remains for ladies wrestling
is this much.

800
01:02:19,268 --> 01:02:21,600
And for this much,
you bought me a box of sweets.

801
01:02:23,773 --> 01:02:25,707
But you have our
complete support.

802
01:02:31,781 --> 01:02:34,614
The reason lndia
doesn't win medals,

803
01:02:35,151 --> 01:02:38,120
is because officers like you
are warming these seats.

804
01:02:38,454 --> 01:02:40,217
Alright. I'll get up.

805
01:02:40,757 --> 01:02:43,385
Titu, serve me lunch.

806
01:02:45,428 --> 01:02:48,295
Mahavir Singh-ji,
care to join me for lunch?

807
01:02:54,337 --> 01:02:57,534
The Federation is a breeding ground
for such termites.

808
01:02:59,041 --> 01:03:01,532
They have ruined sports.

809
01:03:06,983 --> 01:03:10,248
There is no support
for sports persons,

810
01:03:11,154 --> 01:03:14,715
only abuses when you don't win.

811
01:03:15,525 --> 01:03:18,619
Medalists don't grow on trees.

812
01:03:19,195 --> 01:03:21,322
You have to nurture them.

813
01:03:22,165 --> 01:03:25,623
With love, with hard work,
with passion.

814
01:03:29,138 --> 01:03:33,234
And here, the scoundrels don't
give money for even a mat.

815
01:03:34,310 --> 01:03:36,278
What is a mat, brother?

816
01:03:36,512 --> 01:03:40,175
Synthetic mattresses
on which wrestlers fight.

817
01:03:41,717 --> 01:03:44,743
A mattress is a mattress!

818
01:03:47,356 --> 01:03:48,482
No?

819
01:03:49,625 --> 01:03:51,149
Did I say something wrong?

820
01:04:01,103 --> 01:04:04,072
Uncle had already ruined
our sleep, figuratively speaking.

821
01:04:04,340 --> 01:04:07,707
Now he was hell bent
on doing it literally, too.

822
01:04:22,258 --> 01:04:25,557
Wrestling on a mat is different
from mud-wrestling.

823
01:04:26,128 --> 01:04:28,255
Now we have to wrestle
on the mat.

824
01:04:28,364 --> 01:04:31,333
And in mat-wrestling
you have to score points.

825
01:04:31,400 --> 01:04:36,360
You can score one, two,
three or five points.

826
01:04:37,406 --> 01:04:38,464
Omkar...

827
01:04:42,612 --> 01:04:45,103
If you hold the opponent
by the waist,

828
01:04:45,181 --> 01:04:47,149
and drop him to his knees,

829
01:04:47,350 --> 01:04:49,341
then you score one point.

830
01:04:49,552 --> 01:04:54,046
And from the ground position
if you roll him on to his back,

831
01:04:54,123 --> 01:04:55,454
then you score two points.

832
01:04:55,725 --> 01:04:57,488
There are different ways
to do this.

833
01:04:57,660 --> 01:04:58,558
Uncle!

834
01:04:58,628 --> 01:05:01,096
Like this.

835
01:05:01,497 --> 01:05:04,955
Or from the ground position,
like this!

836
01:05:07,570 --> 01:05:13,975
If you flip your opponent on his back
from a standing position,

837
01:05:14,043 --> 01:05:16,204
then you will score three points.

838
01:05:17,446 --> 01:05:18,743
Please, uncle!

839
01:05:19,081 --> 01:05:20,571
Like this... three points.

840
01:05:20,983 --> 01:05:24,316
Like this... from standing position...
on to his back.

841
01:05:24,387 --> 01:05:28,448
To score five points is difficult,
but it can be done.

842
01:05:29,191 --> 01:05:31,386
If you flip your opponent
from a standing position,

843
01:05:31,761 --> 01:05:34,525
above your head
in a rainbow-like arc,

844
01:05:34,764 --> 01:05:36,254
and have him fall on his back,

845
01:05:36,465 --> 01:05:38,262
then you score five points!

846
01:05:38,534 --> 01:05:39,193
Watch.

847
01:05:39,268 --> 01:05:40,064
No... no, please, uncle!

848
01:05:40,136 --> 01:05:41,194
Come here.
- No, please.

849
01:05:46,442 --> 01:05:48,433
A real wrestling mat is not like this.

850
01:05:50,279 --> 01:05:51,712
It's like this.

851
01:06:09,165 --> 01:06:11,599
We have to fight
in the yellow area.

852
01:06:20,276 --> 01:06:22,608
The red zone is a danger area.

853
01:06:23,980 --> 01:06:27,211
If you step out of it,
you lose a point.

854
01:06:34,490 --> 01:06:37,653
There are three rounds
of two minutes each.

855
01:06:38,461 --> 01:06:41,225
Three rounds
of two minutes each.

856
01:06:42,631 --> 01:06:46,567
Whoever wins two out of
three rounds, wins the match.

857
01:06:52,008 --> 01:06:54,408
Sir, your daughter is underweight.

858
01:06:55,478 --> 01:06:56,172
So?

859
01:06:56,579 --> 01:06:57,705
Take my advice.
Go back.

860
01:06:58,280 --> 01:07:00,441
Feed her,

861
01:07:00,516 --> 01:07:02,984
fatten her and
come back next year.

862
01:07:03,319 --> 01:07:06,311
If she fights like this,
she will break her bones.

863
01:07:07,156 --> 01:07:10,023
You just tell me whether
she is allowed to wrestle or not.

864
01:07:11,060 --> 01:07:13,392
Yes... she is.

865
01:07:13,562 --> 01:07:15,223
Sign up.

866
01:07:18,200 --> 01:07:21,636
"Sub-Junior Nationals"

867
01:07:24,607 --> 01:07:25,403
Good move!

868
01:07:39,221 --> 01:07:42,190
Geeta had defeated beefy boys,

869
01:07:42,425 --> 01:07:45,189
how long could these girls survive?

870
01:07:48,264 --> 01:07:49,561
Is that a girl or a storm?

871
01:07:56,405 --> 01:08:00,933
"Sub-Junior National Champion"

872
01:08:01,377 --> 01:08:03,311
"Junior Nationals"

873
01:08:03,446 --> 01:08:04,435
Is she underweight?

874
01:08:04,613 --> 01:08:07,411
Yes... but how does it matter?

875
01:08:31,240 --> 01:08:37,577
"Junior National Champion"

876
01:08:52,027 --> 01:08:55,326
Time flew by.

877
01:08:57,466 --> 01:08:59,730
Geeta went from junior to senior.

878
01:09:01,637 --> 01:09:02,535
And uncle,

879
01:09:02,972 --> 01:09:05,463
from senior to senior-citizen.

880
01:09:09,378 --> 01:09:10,936
Go... Geeta!

881
01:09:12,681 --> 01:09:16,481
Babita and I, went from
shorts to full length pants!

882
01:09:40,543 --> 01:09:42,238
Push... push her down!

883
01:09:45,414 --> 01:09:47,075
Side throw!

884
01:10:00,996 --> 01:10:03,396
Victory to Haryana!

885
01:10:25,521 --> 01:10:27,284
"National Champion"

886
01:10:46,275 --> 01:10:48,573
Finally uncle's dream
has been achieved.

887
01:10:49,044 --> 01:10:51,569
Now we can all relax.

888
01:10:51,780 --> 01:10:52,508
No.

889
01:10:54,783 --> 01:10:56,375
My dream remains to be fulfilled.

890
01:10:58,220 --> 01:11:01,519
Every year sees
a National champion.

891
01:11:02,191 --> 01:11:04,591
My dream will be fulfilled,

892
01:11:05,060 --> 01:11:06,652
when you win gold,
not for yourself,

893
01:11:07,296 --> 01:11:09,196
but for your country.

894
01:11:13,335 --> 01:11:15,303
You can celebrate today.

895
01:11:15,571 --> 01:11:18,506
From tomorrow we start
preparing further.

896
01:11:24,380 --> 01:11:25,540
Papa...

897
01:11:29,051 --> 01:11:31,019
Need to speak to you.

898
01:11:31,720 --> 01:11:32,652
Tell me.

899
01:11:33,322 --> 01:11:34,414
Papa,

900
01:11:35,257 --> 01:11:39,057
now that I am a
National champion, so...

901
01:11:40,696 --> 01:11:41,560
So?

902
01:11:41,664 --> 01:11:43,097
No, I mean,

903
01:11:43,165 --> 01:11:47,431
all National champions
need to go to Patiala,

904
01:11:47,469 --> 01:11:49,164
for further training.

905
01:11:49,705 --> 01:11:51,229
To the National Sports Academy.

906
01:11:51,307 --> 01:11:52,706
What are you getting at?

907
01:11:52,775 --> 01:11:54,174
Tell me clearly.

908
01:11:55,344 --> 01:11:57,335
I will have to go too, papa.

909
01:11:58,647 --> 01:12:01,980
From now, I'll have to train there,

910
01:12:04,186 --> 01:12:06,450
under the national coach.

911
01:12:21,003 --> 01:12:22,470
Geeta Kumari Phogat.

912
01:12:22,638 --> 01:12:24,037
Wrestling.

913
01:12:42,758 --> 01:12:44,282
The place looks good.

914
01:12:46,595 --> 01:12:48,426
Let's hope the coach is good too.

915
01:12:53,369 --> 01:12:54,802
Girls, come on.

916
01:13:00,142 --> 01:13:02,337
You all must be rejoicing,

917
01:13:02,678 --> 01:13:05,306
at the thought of
advanced training.

918
01:13:08,250 --> 01:13:09,410
Well, forget about learning,

919
01:13:10,252 --> 01:13:12,186
first you have to learn to forget!

920
01:13:12,588 --> 01:13:14,715
Forget the wrong training
you've received.

921
01:13:15,190 --> 01:13:17,215
Wrong diet, wrong exercise,
wrong technique.

922
01:13:17,459 --> 01:13:20,053
And after forgetting all that,

923
01:13:20,295 --> 01:13:21,660
your real training will begin,

924
01:13:22,264 --> 01:13:24,459
with National Coach,
Pramod Kadam.

925
01:13:25,701 --> 01:13:29,330
And you will only learn
what I teach you.

926
01:13:31,140 --> 01:13:32,630
Is that clear?
- Yes, sir!

927
01:13:33,075 --> 01:13:35,305
Is that clear?
- Yes, sir!

928
01:13:35,677 --> 01:13:36,439
Good.

929
01:13:37,513 --> 01:13:38,480
Warm up.

930
01:13:39,148 --> 01:13:40,410
Get me tea!

931
01:13:43,152 --> 01:13:44,244
Come on, girls.

932
01:13:44,319 --> 01:13:47,152
Energy... more energy!

933
01:13:47,356 --> 01:13:49,085
Yes, that's the way.

934
01:13:49,158 --> 01:13:50,022
Keep it up!

935
01:13:51,026 --> 01:13:51,492
Good.

936
01:13:51,560 --> 01:13:53,027
Namaste, sir.

937
01:13:53,729 --> 01:13:56,061
Sir, I'm Mahavir Singh Phogat.

938
01:13:56,198 --> 01:13:57,665
Geeta's father.

939
01:13:58,801 --> 01:13:59,529
Okay.

940
01:13:59,768 --> 01:14:01,633
I'm the one who has trained her.

941
01:14:01,970 --> 01:14:04,097
Yes... good.

942
01:14:06,008 --> 01:14:06,975
She's good.

943
01:14:07,042 --> 01:14:09,704
Very strong, with a lot of stamina.

944
01:14:13,081 --> 01:14:15,174
Where's my tea?

945
01:14:16,752 --> 01:14:18,219
Come on... move it!

946
01:14:26,028 --> 01:14:27,256
Sir... one request.

947
01:14:29,031 --> 01:14:31,261
If Geeta gets the right coaching,

948
01:14:31,433 --> 01:14:33,731
she will definitely win
an international medal.

949
01:14:36,171 --> 01:14:37,297
Geeta!

950
01:14:39,675 --> 01:14:43,736
There should be a 90 degree
angle between your calf and thigh.

951
01:14:44,246 --> 01:14:46,305
Who has taught you?

952
01:14:48,116 --> 01:14:50,311
Is this how you will win
an international medal?

953
01:14:55,290 --> 01:14:57,485
You came to drop her, right?

954
01:14:58,060 --> 01:14:59,391
You've done that.

955
01:15:01,029 --> 01:15:02,257
Now leave the rest to me.

956
01:15:04,199 --> 01:15:05,666
Don't waste my time!

957
01:15:44,506 --> 01:15:45,666
Is Geeta happy?

958
01:15:48,577 --> 01:15:51,137
The institute must be
very big, isn't it?

959
01:15:54,049 --> 01:15:56,745
Everyone there must be
a champion, isn't it?

960
01:15:58,687 --> 01:16:00,382
And the facilities there
must be amazing, right?

961
01:16:00,489 --> 01:16:01,581
Have you trained today?

962
01:16:01,723 --> 01:16:04,021
Yes. And the coach
must be top notch?

963
01:16:04,192 --> 01:16:05,989
You seem very eager
to go there.

964
01:16:08,397 --> 01:16:10,262
Remember, I'm still your coach.

965
01:16:12,634 --> 01:16:14,499
Your first time
away from home?

966
01:16:16,238 --> 01:16:19,503
Just you wait...
we'll have a blast.

967
01:16:21,410 --> 01:16:23,708
Girls, 'DDLJ' is showing on TV.

968
01:16:24,146 --> 01:16:24,737
Wow!

969
01:16:25,380 --> 01:16:26,677
Let's watch.

970
01:16:27,015 --> 01:16:28,175
I'm going to sleep.

971
01:16:28,250 --> 01:16:30,616
You can't say no
to Shah Rukh Khan.

972
01:16:31,053 --> 01:16:32,315
It's a sin.

973
01:16:32,454 --> 01:16:33,182
Come.

974
01:16:36,992 --> 01:16:41,656
"Raj, if this girl loves you,
she will turn to look at you."

975
01:16:42,664 --> 01:16:43,528
Please turn.

976
01:16:45,534 --> 01:16:46,523
"Turn."

977
01:16:47,035 --> 01:16:48,024
Turn.

978
01:16:51,373 --> 01:16:52,431
Turn.

979
01:16:53,342 --> 01:16:54,309
"Turn."

980
01:16:55,243 --> 01:16:57,643
She turned!

981
01:17:09,358 --> 01:17:13,021
Just grow your hair.
You will kill it.

982
01:17:13,595 --> 01:17:15,290
A rhino uses strength,

983
01:17:15,397 --> 01:17:18,560
but the tiger uses both
strength and technique.

984
01:17:19,034 --> 01:17:21,093
Be a tiger, not a rhino.

985
01:17:21,203 --> 01:17:22,033
Clear?

986
